# Implementation Plan - SustainaBuy Release 0.3 🚀

This plan outlines the steps to elevate SustainaBuy from a prototype to a polished, functional product comparison and sustainability engine.

## 1. Visual & UI Refinement
Refining the premium aesthetic with subtle animations and better centering.

### Component: [Header & Avatar]
- [MODIFY] [Navbar.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/components/layout/Navbar.tsx): Replace letter avatar with `img` support. Use global [AuthContext](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/contexts/AuthContext.tsx#14-21) to sync profile picture instantly. Center the avatar in its container.

### Component: [Landing Page]
- [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/app/page.tsx): Fix Hero search bar layout based on user feedback. Connect search input to router.
- [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/app/globals.css):
    - Tone down parallax variables.
    - Add `.animate-pulse-dot` for the AI status.
    - Add `@keyframes` for the "Consciously" gradient sweep.

---

## 2. Advanced Search & Product Engine
Transitioning from matching raw strings to a structured product/variant hierarchy (Idealo style).

### Component: [Search System]
- [MODIFY] [db.ts](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/lib/db.ts):
    - Implement `searchProducts(query: string)` that returns a list of results.
    - Add normalization logic (lowercase, trim, regex for typos).
- [NEW] [SearchDropdown.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/components/search/SearchDropdown.tsx): A shared component for the header and landing page to show live results.

### Component: [Product Grouping]
- [MODIFY] Product interfaces to support `variants[]` and `offers[]`.
- [MODIFY] [ProductCard.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/components/product/ProductCard.tsx): Show "Starts from $X" and the Sustainability Score badge prominently.

---

## 3. AI Scanner & Performance Fixes
Eliminating infinite loaders and optimizing slow calculations.

### Component: [AI Scanner]
- [MODIFY] [add-product/page.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/app/add-product/page.tsx):
    - Implement parallel API calls for scoring.
    - Replace generic spinner with step-based progress indicators.
    - Add timeout fallback (2 seconds target).

---

## 4. Account & Authentication
Comprehensive profile and link management.

### Component: [Account Settings]
- [MODIFY] [account/page.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/app/account/page.tsx): Add forms for birthday, name, and profile details.
- [MODIFY] [AuthContext.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/contexts/AuthContext.tsx): Add methods for linking/unlinking providers and updating email/passwords.

