## 5. Content & Footer Pages
Completing the site structure.

- [NEW] [Privacy Policy, Careers, About Us pages].
- [MODIFY] [Footer.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/components/layout/Footer.tsx): Wire broken links.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` after each major component fix.
- Test search normalization with various casing and typos.

### Manual Verification
- Verify parallax intensity across different scroll speeds.
- Test "Cheapest First" sorting logic with mock variant data.
- Check avatar sync across at least 3 different pages after an update.
